ufcEvents.title: UFC on ABC 9 Whittaker vs de Ridder
ufcEvents.description:
UFC on ABC 8, formerly, UFC Fight Night 260, is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that will take place on July 26, 2025, at the Etihad Arena in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates.

Background
The event will mark the promotion's 21st visit to Abu Dhabi and first since UFC 308 in October 2024.

ufcEvents.title: UFC 320
ufcEvents.description:
UFC 320 (also known as Noche UFC 3) is an upcoming mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that will take place on September 13, 2025, at Arena Guadalajara in Guadalajara, Mexico
The event will mark the promotion's third annual "Noche UFC" event commemorating Mexico's independence day, following September 2023's UFC Fight Night: Grasso vs. Shevchenko 2 and September 2024's UFC 306. Notably, it will be the first of these events to take place in Mexico.[
